        "action": "Remove the 'minimum ban' on drink drivers and replace with a lifetime ban",
        "additional_details": "These dangerous people should be taken off the road for good and the penalties for those who offend should be a lot stricter. An example must be made.\r\nAlmost 1 in 4 drink driving offenders return to court for the same offence in the UK.",
        "background": "Currently the law in the UK states that drink driving offenders MAY GET, 6 months\u2019 imprisonment, \r\nan unlimited fine, a driving ban for at least 1 year (3 years if convicted twice in 10 years)",
